Diane Kurys https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diane_Kurys 0 Diane Kurys (French: [djan kyʁis]; born 3 December 1948) is a French filmmaker and actress. She was born in Lyon, Rhône, France, the younger of two daughters born to Russian-Jewish parents who divorced when she was a child. Several of her films as director are semi-autobiographical.
